        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pick the expert lens to research through. It gathers evidence suited to that lens first (design = tokens·accessibility·contrast; debugging = repro·logs·regressions; QA = tests·acceptance criteria·coverage; security = auth·key handling·exposure surface·threat model; planning = needs·priority·roadmap·trade-offs; marketing = messaging·positioning·channels; analytics = metrics·funnel·insights; operations = deployment·reliability·cost; logic = consistency·invariants·duplication·simplification) to build the report and briefs. Applies to this research only."
